<doc id="613355" wikidata="Q7694397" url="?curid=613355" title="Teenage Head">
<text>Teenage Head can refer to:

* &quot;Teenage Head&quot; (Flamin&#x27; Groovies album), a 1971 album by The Flamin&#x27; Groovies, or the title track of that album
* Teenage Head (band), a 1980s Canadian rock band, who were named after the Flamin&#x27; Groovies album and song
:* &quot;Teenage Head&quot; (Teenage Head album), first release by the band</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q1317512" start="30" end="84" title="Teenage Head (Flamin&amp;#x27; Groovies album)" label="&amp;quot;Teenage Head&amp;quot; (Flamin&amp;#x27; Groovies album)"/>
