*2011 - &quot;Maintenance&quot; (&quot;Coach House Books&quot;)
*2021 - &quot;Bleeding Light&quot; (&quot;Invisible Publishing&quot;)
*2025 - &quot;The Damagers&quot; (&quot;Knopf Canada&quot;)

